Package: mkwebapp
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: curl, file, termux-tools
Homepage: https://github.com/Anon4You/mkwebapp
Description: Tool to create Termux .deb packages for websites
 mkwebapp allows users to easily package a website URL into a
 standard Termux .deb package. It generates the necessary launcher
 script, .desktop file, and attempts to fetch an icon, creating a
 seamless integration for Termux:X11 desktop environments.
